<div class="changelog-container">
    <header class="changelog-header">
        <h1>Jukebar Changelog</h1>
        <p>Track all the latest updates, fixes, and improvements</p>
    </header>

    <section class="version-block">
        <div class="version-header">
            <h2>v2.0.1</h2>
            <span class="release-date">04/01/26</span>
        </div>
        <div class="changes">
            <h3>What's new?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Added a Clear Queue History feature to clear your queue history</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug where the leaderboard discount wasn't applying correctly</li>
                <li>Fixed the issue with the queue metadata not updating and pulling old songs with the wrong name and wrong skip shield count</li>
                <li>Known issue: When queueing a song, it might queue Poo Bum Poo Bum 4. We are working on a fix for this.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>